{
    "json_version": 0x2,
    "name": "EVENT_MESSAGE_QC13_ODI_060.ebm",
    "nb_messages": 0x23,
    "messages": [
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x199,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x0,
            "msg_string": "Oh, hello, Ms. Odelia. I came to play."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0xd,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Let us omit the greetings. What is your purpose for coming here today?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "Oh, to do a little research in the library, and to talk to Ms. Odelia..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0xd,
            "extra_id": 0x14e,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "Anything else?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15e,
            "expr_id": 0x5,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "Eh? Umm, if Mr. Keith is here, I'd like to talk to him, too..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0xd,
            "extra_id": 0x150,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "You should have had a much more important reason for coming here."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x160,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "Important...? Oh, that's right!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0xd,
            "extra_id": 0xac,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "Yes, that is it!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "I came to ask if I can keep borrowing the book I borrowed!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0xd,
            "extra_id": 0x117,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "msg_string": "...Because of overwhelming disappointment and despair, I thought I was about to malfunction."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0xd,
            "extra_id": 0x118,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0xa,
            "msg_string": "Ayesha, I completely expected you to have brought sweets with you..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x195,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xb,
            "msg_string": "Oh, that's right! Now that I think about it, that was my most important reason for coming!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0xd,
            "extra_id": 0x119,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xc,
            "msg_string": "Really!? ...As I have told you before, there is no need for me to eat."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0xd,
            "extra_id": 0xad,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0xd,
            "msg_string": "So, looking forward for Ayesha's arrival with the desire to partake in her sweets, or..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0xd,
            "extra_id": 0xae,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0xe,
            "msg_string": "Going to the entrance, thinking that it might be about time that Ayesha would come..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0xd,
            "extra_id": 0xaf,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xf,
            "msg_string": "I can certainly declare that those activities never happened."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x10,
            "msg_string": "Hmhmhm, I understand. Then I'll prepare some for you right away."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x11,
            "msg_string": "Oh, I know! Ms. Odelia, do you think you can prepare some tea?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0xd,
            "extra_id": 0x14e,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x12,
            "msg_string": "Tea? Its association with sweets is not recognized."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x13,
            "msg_string": "That's not true. Tea and sweets go very well together."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x14,
            "msg_string": "It's like they enhance each other.<CR>Tea boosts sweets even further!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0xd,
            "extra_id": 0x150,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x15,
            "msg_string": "I-Is that true? Then I must immediately respond to that accordingly."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0xd,
            "extra_id": 0x30,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x16,
            "msg_string": "I shall prepare the tea. Ayesha, please start the unveiling of the sweets!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x17,
            "msg_string": "Thank you for the tea.<CR>That was sooo good!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0xd,
            "extra_id": 0x73,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x18,
            "msg_string": "The association between tea and sweets...is very mysterious."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0xd,
            "extra_id": 0x74,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x19,
            "msg_string": "The causal relationship between the both is not recognized. However, what Ayesha said was true."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0xd,
            "extra_id": 0x74,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x1a,
            "msg_string": "When objects α and β mix together to create the completely different situation, γ... It is very mysterious."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0xd,
            "extra_id": 0x75,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1b,
            "msg_string": "Sweets brought a bright color to me when my times were gray."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1c,
            "msg_string": "I see. Ms. Odelia, you've been here for hundreds of years..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x195,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1d,
            "msg_string": "Okay, I've decided! I'll continue to bring you sweets from now on, as well!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1e,
            "msg_string": "Is there anything else you want to eat?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0xd,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1f,
            "msg_string": "Well...I would like to try anything,<CR>as long as it is a sweet..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0xd,
            "extra_id": 0x30,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x20,
            "msg_string": "However, I would also like to experience the object known as cream."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x193,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x21,
            "msg_string": "Sweets with cream it is. Got it!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x76,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x22,
            "msg_string": "(All right, I'm totally getting excited!)"
        }
    ]
}